text: When exiting from the carpark, a Malay security guard was standing at the gantry made a comment : ‘Wha park whole day here, here is private parking’

The cuppachino and the mocha latte taste extremely good. I like the salmon sandwich but today sold out so I took the egg mayo with the bread toasted to perfection and still hot when u bite on it. Give it a thump up
